    "title": "SeaKing B03 Fiberglass Fillet Table (L32.7\" x W16.9\") & 2 Game Rated Rod Holders",
    "body_html": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Crafted for anglers who appreciate tradition and quality, the SeaKing SK-B01 and SK-B03 <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-441c5c2f-7fff-8a29-97d9-ed4e18b4acb2\">Fiberglass Fillet Table (Also known as Bait Boards)</b> </span><span>feature a UV resistant PE plastic cutting board, a convenient sink with drain for storage, </span><span>and robust 316 marine grade stainless steel hardware. These boards are meticulously handmade </span><span>using top-grade composite materials for durability and reliability on the water. Ideal for serious </span><span>fishermen, these fillet table offer exceptional functionality and enduring craftsmanship, ensuring they </span><span>stand up to the rigors of marine environments while providing essential features for a successful day </span><span>of fishing.</span><strong></strong></p>",
